org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.queue.AeInboundReceive

Packages that use AeInboundReceive
org.activebpel.rt.bpel This package contains classes for creating a BPEL model and for implements a standalone BPEL engine for testing designs. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl This package contains the base classes used in the implementation model for the BPEL activities. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.queue Contains classes that model inbound and outbound messages from the engine as well as alarms.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.storage Classes related to saving and restoring the state of processes.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.visitors Classes that visit a tree of BPEL implementation objects and save or restore their state.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine The BPEL engine, support classes, and engine factory.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.process This package contains classes related to process management.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.recovery This package contains classes for recovering or regenerating the state of a process from alarms, messages, or faults that the process received. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.recovery.journal This package contains classes for representing journal entries for alarms, messages, or faults for possible recovery in the event of engine failure. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.recovery.test This package contains classes for testing the functionality of the recovery engine. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage This package contains classes for storing the state of BPEL processes to an external storage facility. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.providers   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.sql This package contains classes for storing the state of BPEL processes to a SQL database. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.xmldb.queue Contains the storage classes that implement a XMLDB version of the Queue storage.
